data.description: WATERFRONT!!! DON’T MISS OUT TO OWN THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME! This home is EXTREMELY RARE and a true GEM in the HIGHLY DESIRABLE community of LONG LAKE RANCH. Offering WATERFRONT/CONSERVATION VIEWS and Breathtaking Sunrises while sipping your favorite beverage. This executive home features 4 bedrooms,3 baths, hard to find 3 car garage, office/gym and LARGE BONUS ROOM/HOME THEATER or IN-LAW SUITE WITH SEPARATE MASTER BEDROOM/BATH. With it's open floor plan, high ceilings, large CHEF INSPIRED gourmet kitchen, oversize bar all with granite countertops, large walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, and breakfast bar this home has it all!. The kitchen opens to a spacious family room, sliding glass doors open to a large private screened lanai and extended patio with brick pavers. The huge master suite has volume ceilings, ensuite master bath with granite countertops, large walk-in closet, dual sinks, walk-in shower and soaking tub. Enjoy the peace & tranquility of your backyard with beautiful conservation views with plenty of space to enjoy BBQ’s with family & friends! Experience the Florida lifestyle that features a sparkling pool and lastly a large yard surrounded by privacy fence round out this IMMACULATE home. Long Lake Ranch is a wonderful community, amenities include a resort style community pool with splash pad, fishing dock, playground, tennis/pickelball courts, basketball courts and dog park. Located in an A-RATED School District and close to shopping/dining/beaches/golf courses and easy access to Veteran’s Expressway with a quick 30 min commute to Tampa International Airport and downtown Tampa. A MUST SEE! CALL TODAY FOR A PRIVATE TOUR OF THIS STUNNING HOME!
